    },
    {
      "locale": "zhCN",
      "text": "“怎么不说话了？也许这样反倒更明智。”",
      "modification_date": "2026-04-28T08:25:08.4866006Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2026-04-28T08:25:08.4866007Z",
      "original_text": "\"Staying silent? Perhaps that's for the best.\"",
